name: Qpid JMS
description:
Apache Qpid JMS - A new AMQP 1.0 JMS client built around the Qpid Proton library, and implementing the JMS Mapping for AMQP as it evolves at OASIS.


Please refer to https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPID for issues with previous JMS clients released by the Qpid project.
